      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding challenge! This vehicle is the ultimate project for a dedicated DIYer or someone looking for a valuable source of parts. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back on the road, it offers a fantastic foundation for a complete restoration at a budget-friendly price!",
